name: Dodge the Game Engines
description:
This is a game where some machine/engines fall down. You have to dodge them.

ENJOY the game and share your highest score in the comments! 

This game is fully AI created!  But the music is taken from Unity Asset Store (Save/Pause Music- Royalty Free). You can play this game on mobiles too!

This game is ad free and I have not implemented ads. As this game is AI created, there might be some mistakes (such as the highscore). 

NOTE: You can make gameplay videos of this game and upload on social media.

And donate if possible :)
